{"tid":1025205,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙銀行就凍結華人賬戶致歉 惟否認歧視","createTime":"2019-02-17T07:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T07:43:28.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c448089bcf2d6206539201f0aac8862c85e94a39","tid":1025205,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/02/17/2060607_23d918fd8116e688667148743a3021a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F02%2F17%2F2060607_23d918fd8116e688667148743a3021a5.jpg&h=2b0ceb9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西班牙第二大銀行BBVA就凍結數百名當地華人的賬戶致歉，但否認歧視，強調只是按當地的反洗黑錢法例行事。<br />\n<br />\nBBVA發表聲明稱，對於過去數天凍結一些客戶的賬戶造成不便致歉，已推出措施紓緩有關影響，又重申反對任何形式的不合理歧視。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙銀行業協會(AEB)發言人Jos&eacute; Luis Mart&iacute;nez Campuzano指出，為符合國家的反洗黑錢法例，銀行需要「監察與控制客戶」。顧客必須提供法律規定的所有資料予銀行。銀行正努力加快程序，讓情況恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙去年通過法例加強打擊洗黑錢，規定顧客要向銀行遞交更多個人資料，但當地華人組織批評中國顧客所需的程序比當地人複雜。<br />\n<br />\n組織聲稱，多達5000人的賬戶被凍結，形容無法生活。<br />\n<br />\n上周五，數百名當地華人在馬德里BBVA總部外抗議銀行歧視。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2060607/%E8%A5%BF%E7%8F%AD%E7%89%99%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%E8%8F%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AC%E6%88%B6%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89+%E6%83%9F%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2060607%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%258F%25AD%25E7%2589%2599%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25AC%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%2589%2B%25E6%2583%259F%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25AD%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxhVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=6897d331\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2060607/%E8%A5%BF%E7%8F%AD%E7%89%99%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%E8%8F%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AC%E6%88%B6%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89+%E6%83%9F%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96</a>"}]}